{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/7574275.Victor_Noble", "name": "Victor Noble", "genres": ["Spirituality", "Contemporary", "Religion"], "avg_rating": 4.42, "num_reviews": 12, "num_ratings": 59, "about": "After spending the best part of his life, sincerely trying to find answers to life\u2019s basic questions in scientific explanations, religious texts, and spiritual practices; Victor gave up on his quest, due to sheer exhaustion, in early 2007. A few weeks later, he had an experience of spiritual awakening. Soon afterward, he started sharing his insights in question-answer sessions to a small group of friends; he is now regularly invited to such sessions by spiritual seekers and friends in Sydney, Australia and wherever else he travels.In 2011, he started writing short pieces to read at these Q&amp;A sessions; the purpose of a reading was to set the tone for the enquiry that followed. With help and encouragement from friends, a selec After spending the best part of his life, sincerely trying to find answers to life\u2019s basic questions in scientific explanations, religious texts, and spiritual practices; Victor gave up on his quest, due to sheer exhaustion, in early 2007. A few weeks later, he had an experience of spiritual awakening. Soon afterward, he started sharing his insights in question-answer sessions to a small group of friends; he is now regularly invited to such sessions by spiritual seekers and friends in Sydney, Australia and wherever else he travels.In 2011, he started writing short pieces to read at these Q&amp;A sessions; the purpose of a reading was to set the tone for the enquiry that followed. With help and encouragement from friends, a selection of these writings are now compiled and published as Letters from your soul. ...more"}
