{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/13654965.Durgesh_Satpathy", "name": "Durgesh Satpathy", "genres": ["Nonfiction", "Self Help", "Psychology"], "avg_rating": 3.91, "num_reviews": 14, "num_ratings": 211, "about": "Durgesh Satpathy is an author, management consultant, and an academician. He has done MBA from Nagpur University and PG Diploma in Psychological Counseling from Madurai Kamaraj University. He aims to reform the mindsets of people through his writing.He is also a psychological counselor and mentor to students. He can be reached at: www.facebook.com/Sdurgesh, www.twitter.com/authordurgesh, or info@durgeshsatpathy.com"}
