protagonists, Knight, literally hanging off a cliff staring into the stony eyes of a trilobite embedded in the rock that has been dead for millions of years. This became the archetypal \u2014 and literal \u2014 cliff-hanger of Victorian prose.Excerpted from Wikipedia. ...more"}
