. She was 69.David Eddings died on June 2, 2009 at the age of 77. ...more"}
{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/18819083.Maricar_Banguis", "name": "Maricar Banguis", "genres": ["Children's", "Fiction", "Fantasy"], "avg_rating": 5.0, "num_reviews": 2, "num_ratings": 29, "about": "Maricar Banguis has always been interested in fantasy stories, adventures and traveling. When she was a child, she loved playing in nature and imagining she was in a magical land where people could fly.Maricar is now a happy wife and proud mother. She loves the outdoors and spending time with her family. She enjoys telling stories to her daughter."}
